{"tid":1555407,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BBC牽頭 媒體巨擘聯手打擊假新聞","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T00:49:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"234d21905c4bef7d45d99674b1a5f31f8cba2a2c","tid":1555407,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190908/20764447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F20764447&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BugEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=e9970b3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F20764447&h=bfecddea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190908/20764447</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年09月08日<br />\nBBC牽頭 媒體巨擘聯手打擊假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190908/large/1567877055_f59b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190908%2Flarge%2F1567877055_f59b.gif&h=76df15ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對網絡年代假資訊假新聞氾濫，英國廣播公司（BBC）（圖）近日倡議一項打擊假資訊計劃，獲法新社、路透社等10多間國際傳媒機構與科技巨擘響應支持，初步提出的行動包括設立假新聞預警制度，以及加強教育等。<br />\n<br />\nBBC今夏舉行了一次「可信新聞高峯會」，號召全球科技與傳媒機構合作應對假資訊氾濫危機，共同研擬出的行動計劃包括在合作夥伴間設立預警制度，一旦發現危害人命、或選舉期間干擾民主的假資訊，即迅速通報，務求盡快將假資訊消滅於微時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包括fb路透社Google<br />\n<br />\n另外各機構亦會攜手辦網上傳媒教育計劃，以及在選舉期間合作發放公民資訊，讓選民獲得清晰的投票機制及票站地點等資料。BBC形容這些都是對抗假資訊的「重要舉措」 ，總經理霍爾（Tony Hall）說：「假資訊和所謂假新聞對我們所有人都構成威脅，最嚴重時更會嚴重威脅民主以至人命。峯會展現出各機構攜手打擊的決心。」行動詳情會在稍後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n迄今已加入計劃的機構包括法新社、路透社、歐洲廣播聯盟、英國《金融時報》（Financial Times）、美國《華爾街日報》（The Wall Street Journal）、《印度教徒報》（The Hindu）、加拿大廣播公司、facebook、Google與微軟。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司/法新社 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n金正恩委任新軍頭 擬開發新武器<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n烏俄交換囚犯 盼「完結可怕戰爭」<br />\n <br />\n蘋果日報fb，每日分享精選新聞及網絡新鮮事。<br />\n<br />\n返回最頂<br />\n <br />\n焦點 全部 要聞 突發 娛樂 兩岸 國際 財經 果籽 飲食男女 體育 賽馬"},{"pid":"c4d7827faf45aec739a388e50ad79c1fe334e37f","tid":1555407,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d03dcf785e48c044757775b419c1cbdba8c877c","tid":1555407,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSIR, fake news comes from THIS WAY, china"},{"pid":"4d74ed85bbe805814a4743447af6d5b9ba89636c","tid":1555407,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d03dcf785e48c044757775b419c1cbdba8c877c","tid":1555407,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSIR, fake news comes from THIS WAY, china"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96870548f8d964de4ef7cbbedf210f3265e8e04f","tid":1555407,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffa869e2fcef366f0d8183718d711e3fb68517e9","tid":1555407,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:23:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"560693edac9b3370eb80a37d20c43dfba9d43452","tid":1555407,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"咪就係中國俄羅斯呢啲垃圾政權發假新聞"},{"pid":"2025